document_data.mainbody: '''Alley Way''' was a street located in the city of [[Zhentil Keep]] during the midâ€“14{{th}} century [[DR]].
document_data.Location: Alley Way was located in southeast Zhentil Keep in the [[Zhentil Keep/Common Quarter|Common Quarter]]. The road branched south then southwest from the midpoint of [[Hasbeen Road]] to terminate along [[Vice Street]] and [[Border Street]] near the southern wall of the city.
